{"tid":2162171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從上年抗爭已經睇到中共喺臨垃會嘅陰謀","createTime":"2020-08-18T03:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T07:55:41.000Z","uid":335967,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa3badd4e6f23ea4eef3ee85421e73b614d4828","tid":2162171,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">泛民總辭/留任其實唔會影響中共施政方針。中共最怕嘅係大家團結，最想嘅係內部分化，避開自己出手嘅政治成本。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家睇返2019年抗爭:<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">1. 和理非主導</span><br />\n政府無視訴求&gt;&gt;令更多和理非認同/加入勇武抗爭&gt;&gt;<span class=\"gold\">和勇不分</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">2. 勇武主導</span><br />\n中共放狗咬人&gt;&gt;被國際譴責&gt;&gt;制裁&gt;&gt;<span class=\"gold\">加速主義</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">3. 和勇割席</span><br />\n重演14年佔中，<span class=\"red\">內部分化導致瓦解&gt;&gt; 中共坐享漁人之利</span><br />\n<br />\n再睇下依家臨垃會件事:<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">1. 全體拒絕委任</span><br />\n中共垃會70/70 &gt;&gt; 明日大嶼/辱警罪/健康碼/23條全票通過&gt;&gt;<span class=\"gold\">加速主義</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">2. 全部留任</span><br />\n人大引用基本法附件3 &gt;&gt; <span class=\"red\">明日大嶼/辱警罪/健康碼/23條照樣通過 </span><br />\n<br />\n明年選舉更多本土派/抗爭派取代泛民&gt;&gt;中共被迫全面DQ &gt;&gt; 國際進一步制裁&gt;&gt; <span class=\"gold\">超音速主義</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">3. 去留各半</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">中共成功制造內部分化</span>，另一方面留任議員不足否決人數，徹底失敗。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講句: <span class=\"red\">議會戰線一早就收咗皮</span>，仲話「係議會抵抗惡法」嘅人瞓咗咁耐瞓撚醒未？<span class=\"red\"><strong>無論泛民全體拒絕人大委任，抑或全部留任，中共想過嘅議案一樣過到，議會戰線唯一作用就係逼中共DQ攬炒。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n泛民依家最重要做嘅唔係出乜撚嘢「大多數議員傾向留任，會繼續討論」嘅垃圾聲明，而係<span class=\"red\">強調「 不論最終去留，全體在任議員必定齊上齊落」， 體現對抗中共嘅團結。 </span>"},{"pid":"a27c99add8c60e651b7ec51b0e160e4a46649e0f","tid":2162171,"uid":63400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"馬後炮！事後孔明！"},{"pid":"955502745d6543563e6d45a1df5e9da06dd253be","tid":2162171,"uid":225100,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGGtm1j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGGtm1j.jpg&h=60901ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vodLV4K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvodLV4K.png&h=572b2e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkrNvaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkrNvaR.jpg&h=bde8db61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhMUUCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhMUUCv.jpg&h=d4a1a316&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38ca28539ab4c92a0365beac9273139d0d75baf4","tid":2162171,"uid":287461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n辭唔辭根本冇分別，惡法一樣過<br />\n想辭就辭想留就留，根本就冇咩分別<br />\n唔分化唔割席"},{"pid":"71eeb5424493c443889ee7b5788c2c71deb16f9d","tid":2162171,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fa3badd4e6f23ea4eef3ee85421e73b614d4828","tid":2162171,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:42:39.000Z","ms