 />\n<br />\n泛民依家最重要做嘅唔係出乜撚嘢「大多數議員傾向留任，會繼續討論」嘅垃圾聲明，而係<span class=\"red\">強調「 不論最終去留，全體在任議員必定齊上齊落」， 體現對抗中共嘅團結。 </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"留任對支共既破壞力比起總辭更加驚人，唔明班人咁快想棄守陣地做乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671256c3cf786db70e8a814b166a4b2ea7e20420","tid":2162171,"uid":299467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3210559336c0a9deb509bd805227c8d9ab6ecb24","tid":2162171,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84dc00effd8060aadf192d74169cd55e38ed049e","tid":2162171,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8e27fb88c0340e8f22acae7766d46018d16637","tid":2162171,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a27c99add8c60e651b7ec51b0e160e4a46649e0f","tid":2162171,"uid":63400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"馬後炮！事後孔明！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:47:32.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae2ddb3d0cc697c4a061a72f8f748b7bfda5afe","tid":2162171,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 